name: Warrior Statement Cuff Bracelet
description:
This edgy statement cuff bracelet is hand forged from copper using the traditional fold-forming technique. With fold forming flat sheet metal is folded and repeatedly hammered, annealed (heated to soften) and hammered some more before unfolding. The "point" that serves as the focal point of this piece is actually the forged fold. The bracelet is then finished with a heat patina to give it a modern, rustic look.

Made to your specified size and shipped within 7 business days. As every bracelet is handmade, please allow for variation in texture and color pattern.

Bracelets are made according to your measurements and are meant to fit your wrist without twisting and turning. Simply measure your wrist, send me the number and I'll hand fabricate your bracelet for the perfect fit!

*** Don't forget to put your wrist measurement in the "Message to Seller" at checkout! ***

Your new custom bracelet will ship to you in a handmade drawstring pouch for safekeeping. Gift boxes shown in final photo are available at no charge upon request, if you'd like a gift box simply note it in the "Message to Seller" at checkout.
